      "_comment": "IMPL-20 #6: BloodReadingRepository.findLatestByMarker — whereEqualTo(marker) + orderBy(sampleDate DESC).limit(1). The bodyComposition entry above already covers BodyCompositionRepository.findLatest (metric ASC, sampleTime DESC). DailyMetricRepository.findLatestDailyMetric only needs the auto-created single-field `date` index, so no composite entry is required for it.",
